        "Description": "An online gift retailer for Valentine hid its true inventory - guns stacked beside humming servers in a deep underground bunker. A calm Negotiator arrived with money, urging the five board members to choose love over blood. They laughed. He didn&apos;t. In one savage sweep, he seized their own guns and cut them down, shredding flesh and server alike. If those weapons had reached couples, lovers would have turned them on each other. It was 47 who made sure they never do.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Zubin47.",
